*** 

In the US $5m Longines Dubai Sheema Classic, Mishriff (David Eagan 2-1), came from the widest starting point, from behind, to see off Japanese raiders, Chrono Genesis and Loves Only You. Only Two necks separated the first three home, in a time of 2:26:6/10. No sign of another favourite, Mogul. Japan's Chuwa Wizard (Keita Tosaki 5-1) finished second. If it happens positively, it will make Frankie Dettori equal Jerry Bailey's win tally Health ministry says the death toll is now 2,117, the cases 130,214 and the positivity rate 16.4 per cent. President Suluhu suspends Deusdedit Kakoko over allegations of massive embezzlement at the ports authority. Authority directs radio station to publish an apology over the offending programme.